phrases: These people would be late for their own mother's funeral.
But I have got somewhere to be.
Every night she digs her nails into my skin.
Let us get to work, then.
The cops could be by at any minute.
It is supposed to be good quality stuff, right?
Fifty grand in cold, hard cash.
Yeah, that is good quality, all right.
You could make some really good drugs with this.
Afraid that is a trade secret, mister.
Now we can finally get to the point.
This is the San-Teresa Metropolitan Police.
You are under arrest for kidnapping and human trafficking.
This fairy is a Semanian citizen.
On your knees, hands above your heads.
You shithead cops set us up!
You have got quite the potty mouth, do not you?
You can do the honors, Kei.
You have the right to remain silent.
Anything that comes out of that foul mouth of yours
may be used against you in a court of law.
You have the right to a lawyer.
If you cannot afford to pay one of those meddling shitheads,
you will be provided a public defender.
So grateful you could cry, right?
The fairy was always meant to come to me.
Fifteen years ago, a hyperspace gate appeared in the middle of the Pacific.
Beyond the gate lay a strange world filled with fairies and monsters.
This city is Earth's front door.
Over two million citizens from this other world live here.
A mixture of different races and diverse cultures, haves and have-nots...
The world's newest city of dreams.
But in the shadows of all this chaos lurked countless crimes.
The San-Teresa Metropolitan Police maintained a special unit to deal with these crimes.
Matoba, they found the perp's body.
-It was lying on the road in Apple Hills.
Chief Roth, I got three clean hits with a 9mm.
No way in hell he made it that far.
If he was a normal criminal, no.
It was one of those goddamn aliens.
So he was being controlled by a Semanian wizard, you think?
The perp was speaking in Farbani.
Using vocab from their intellectual class.
He said that fairy was special.
I will get things in order.
My partner of four years was just killed.
I am going to find him and make him pay.
That is an order, Sergeant Matoba.
I am sorry about what happened to Rick.
But that is why you need to get some rest.
What the hell am I supposed to tell his wife?
I want your report on my desk by 9:00 AM tomorrow.
Mister, I will wash your car for you.
If you do not pay it, your car might get banged up.
Now, where did I put it?
Earth may be weak, but there are scary people here.
There is been a change of plans.
I need you to go meet a noble for me.
A VIP from the Farbani Kingdom is arriving early tomorrow morning.
You want me to go meet some alien noble?
We do not have enough detectives who can speak their language.
Let me hunt down the guy who killed Rick.
The VIP might be involved in this.
I have already talked to the coast guard.
We are almost to the gate.
You ever been to their world?
I was stuffed inside a transport plane, so I did not get to see the gate itself.
Nobody can see the Mirage Gate.
We need to rely on information from our observation satellites.
But those damn aliens can tell where the gate is
just by looking at the wind and tides.
And do a damn sight better job than we can.
And that is why the coast guard's always busy?
If we wanted to catch all the smugglers and illegal immigrants,
we would need twice the funding and manpower.
It is some important noble, right?
I will let you deal with them.
I am Exedilica, of the Knights of Mirvor.
Do Earth sailors not even have the ritual of welcoming?
Do you not know how to talk?
Tilarna Barsh Mirvor Imsedalya Iyeh Tebreina Devol Nelano Seiya Nel Exedilica!
In your Earth language, that means
Tilarna, eldest daughter of Seiya, of the House of Exedilica,
heir to the bloodline of Duke Devol, of the glorious Knights of Mirvor.
No, people of low birth often have short names.
I will not let it bother me.
I usually go by Tilarna Exedilica.
Now, carry my things, Kay Imatuba.
Did you not hear me, Sergeant Matoba?
You will be working with her from now on.
You will be doing your investigations with her.
She will take Sergeant Fury's place.
You want me to work with this alien?
He does not understand the circumstances.
She came here to find that fairy.
That fairy is the equivalent of a VIP in the Semani world.
It was kidnapped there and brought here by smugglers.
She is a Farbanian knight sent here to recover the fairy.
In accordance with our treaty with the country called The United Nations,
the Knights of Mirvor are given the right to dispense justice on Earth.
I, Tilarna Exedilica, request your help in the name of the Farbani Kingdom.
Rick was my partner for four years, and now he is dead!
And now I am supposed to babysit some kid?
Your order can go eat shit!
Chief Roth, do not you want to avenge Rick?
I have known Rick for 20 years.
I am telling you to do this because it is necessary.
Do you need any more explanation than that?
It appears that my own will is being ignored.
I want to work with the best boliceman your city has to offer.
I cannot imagine a rude boor like this acting as my guard.
No, he will be your partner.
Or do you want a man
whose etiquette is perfect, but who is otherwise completely useless?
If so, I do not think you will be getting your fairy back.
I said do not touch it.
He was too scared to say much, though.
From a gang of Mexicans in a Ridgeline.
Sounds like he does not know their names.
We are going to find the fairy's original owners.
There cannot be that many Mexican gangs in Ridgelines running around.
Just shut up and sit there.
Are you trying to get me killed?
Please, just do not do anything!
I am not taking orders from you.
I am going with you, Kay Imatuba.
Just try to walk as far away from me as possible.
I do not want anyone thinking we are friends.
Hey, we do not open until seven.
He is in the other room on the phone.
Have a good time with her, then.
Hey, did you not hear me?
Did you think I would get scared and beg for help?
Yes, this should be a good deal for us both.
This gift of 50 51-inch TVs brought to us by these sinful
young children is truly a blessing from God.
It is a theological analogy for God's grace.
Blessings of God be with you!
Feeling the breath of God today?
O'Neill, I am looking for a Mexican gang.
They are a violent bunch, and I would rather not anger them if possible...
But perhaps a sufficiently large donation could make God
A donation of around 300 dollars, specifically.
If you do not know anything,
you will have to deal with the goddess of the courtroom
You are on probation, are not you?
That is an illegal threat, Sergeant Matoba!
Someday Satan will get his claws into your soul!
Now, what is this about 51-inch TVs?
Maybe I should go ask the guys in the burglary division?
You are willing to believe the words of a thief?
O'Neill may be a criminal, but he does not like drugs or murder.
He can be trusted... to a degree.
He is a guy you just cannot hate, I guess.
Are not you supposed to be enforcers of justice?
I was told that there were warriors on Earth who fought for the because of justice.
That they helped the needy and fought evil.
That is what you bolicemen are, right?
I honestly had some hopes for you.
But I cannot believe you are making deals with a thief.
In the old days, you would be right, but now...
If there is no word from me in 30 minutes, then you can worry about me.
Yeah, I should have known you would not listen.
Someone controlled by an evil wizard was just here...
Shield of law, protection of the war god.
